Description: Fragment of neck and flattened handle of a Knidian pottery transport amphora to moderate turn. Clay near fine red-brown; some large inclusions. Rectangular stamp with anchor symbol.
Type series: KT1746 (Virginia Grace's unpublished K(nidian) T(ype) series)
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.0340)
